@bigwimpie    "Serials are working, block the app with your firewall, or use the app without internet connection. And don't check for updates. "

To activate the product, you must enter the serial number; to enter the serial number, you must connect to the Uniblue Server to confirm the validity of the aforementioned serial number. If we disconnect from the internet and/or block the program at the firewall, we will be unable to connect to the server, and therefore unable to activate (and use the full version) of the product.

That being said, neither of the 2 serial numbers you provided are valid. I appreciate the time you put into uploading this, but myself and the entire community would fully appreciate instructions that apply, and not just useless uploads, serials, and comments by you, bigwimpie.
